nodes.title: Partner Central
nodes.description: The Partner Central home page presents a high‑level overview of the latest partner‑focused news and resources, featuring headline banners for major announcements such as joint solutions, marketing insights, product availability, and upcoming partner programs. Its primary purpose is to give distributors a quick gateway to current updates, stories, and strategic initiatives that are relevant to their partnership with Cisco, Pure Storage, and Nutanix. Visible sections include a rotating hero carousel of featured announcements and a concise “catch‑up” area that aggregates the newest insights and program information.

nodes.title: Partner Central
nodes.description: The page is a “Sales Data – Bookings” view within Partner Central that lists individual sales opportunities in a tabular format. Its primary function is to let distributors see detailed booking information—such as opportunity identifiers, customer and account details, opportunity type and stage, forecast category, product lineup, and the associated reseller and distributor names. The key visible sections are the page header with navigation controls (including “View As”) and a comprehensive table that organizes each opportunity across the listed columns.

nodes.title: Partner Central
nodes.description: The page is a sales‑data view within Partner Central that lists booking opportunities filtered by the “New Logo” sub‑category. Its primary function is to let distributors see a detailed table of each opportunity—including identifiers, customer and account details, opportunity type and stage, forecast category, product lineup, and the associated reseller and distributor names. The visible sections consist of a header bar with navigation and date controls, followed by the comprehensive opportunities table; no forms or editable fields are present on this screen.

nodes.title: Partner Central
nodes.description: The page is a sales‑data view within Partner Central that lists booking opportunities filtered by the “Expansion” sub‑category. Its primary function is to let distributors see a detailed table of opportunities—including fields such as opportunity name, ID, customer, account segment, type, stage, forecast category, products, and the associated reseller and distributor—so they can review and manage their pipeline. The visible sections consist of the page header with navigation and date controls, followed by the comprehensive opportunities table; no forms or additional interactive widgets are present on this screen.

nodes.title: Partner Central
nodes.description: The page is a “Renewals Data” view within Partner Central that lists booking information in a table format, showing any available renewal opportunities (or indicating when none are present). Its primary function is to let a distributor review and manage renewal bookings associated with their partners. The layout includes a header with navigation controls (e.g., “View As”) and a central table that would display the renewal records when they exist.

nodes.title: Partner Central
nodes.description: The page is a “Sales Data” view within Partner Central that lists booking information for the “Others” sub‑category. Its primary function is to let a distributor see a table of booking opportunities (or a notice when none exist) related to that sub‑category, with navigation elements such as the global header, “View As” selector, and footer. The layout consists of a header bar, a central table area (showing either rows of bookings or a “No opportunities found” message), and standard site navigation/footer links.
